Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: pyhdf
Version: 0.5-1
Summary: Python interface to the NCSA HDF4 library
Home-page: ftp://nordet.qc.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/pub/soft/pyhdf
Author: Andre Gosselin
Author-email: gosselina@dfo-mpo.gc.ca
License: public
Description: The pyhdf package wraps the functionality of the NCSA HDF4 library inside a Python OOP framework. Only the SD API is implemented for now, but other APIs will be covered in the near future. SD variables are read/written through Numeric arrays. netCDF files can also be read and modified with pyhdf.
Keywords: hdf,netcdf,Numeric,python
Platform: UNKNOWN
